  html[data-theme=&#39;dark&#39;] &amp;#123;
    .@&amp;#123;prefix-cls&amp;#125; &amp;#123;
      border: 1px solid rgb(196 188 188);
    &amp;#125;
  &amp;#125;

ps：less还支持动态变量名，6666
